Your level 6 spell question:<P>In your trainer's window it doesn't show the level you are AT, it shows how much you need to SPEND to get to the NEXT level.<P>So, if it says "6" in your trainer window, in your character sills info (the hand button) it will probably say "5".<P>That said, if truly you are at 6 then you must request help from a higher power to give you missing skills.  I had it happen to me once with a spiritmaster I made.<P>--------------------<P>Xarielle Aruspex<BR>Witch of the Laughing Lion<BR>Glastonbury Irregulars - Nimue<BR><I>warm entrails never lie</I>
